reviews.text: The food is average, but the interior design is super cute~

Place is ding dong themed which is cute! 
However the food quality is quite poor and definitely not worth the price.

Hey what’s up food hunters 😎? Wanna eat like a Hongkie(local people)? we went in this place for dinner , we have ordered 3 dinner set , a kabayaki eel set it comes with 2 side dishes and a pot of tea , u have put the tea over the rice the tea actually is soup the eel is fresh well fried and the other set is cook salmon with rice set the set also cones with 2 side dishes and a pot of tea and we also order a kids meal set they have a kids manual too , there is no queue when i get here at 18:30 on weekend, we spend about HK$280 for the dinner average HK$90 per head , OVERALL - clean & neat ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , food quality ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , atmosphere ⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5 , pricing ⭐️⭐️out of 5 , price to food quality ratio ⭐️⭐️⭐️out of 5, if u like my review please hit that LIKE ❤️button thanks and i will see u guys on the next one , love n peace ✌🏻-Detour Guide-
 P.S. u can follow me on Instagram ： detourguides for more Reviews

result.name: Discovery Park

reviews.text: Excellent place for family with kids. Can spend all day here with reasonable cost. Public facilities, shops and entertainment are all well designed with kids in mind. The cinema is even decorated and provided with kids seats and play areas. Coming place is more spacious than you could imagine.
Large mall with wide variety of shops, restaurants, and a cinema, but no supermarket. Great place for families with young kids. Parking is relatively cheap.
Good location, family friendly! Good for shopping with kids

A large and well designed shopping mall. Shops were of large types and properly located at different areas of the mall. Food choices were absurd with a bizarre choice from local fast food to American tastes to top-of-the-class cuisines. A huge recommendation for foodies. Activities there are also never-ending and makes the mall suitable for children and adults of all ages.
Spacious.  Good restaurants.  Convenient supermarket.  Comfortable weeknight visit.
